Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:05.60,Signs,,0,0,0,,Karuizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:17.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes! Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:18.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's just like Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:23.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Too bad about the tennis,\Nbut bowling's also fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:29.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, there's also one guy who is drinking in desperation\Nbecause he can't watch tennis girls in miniskirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're up next, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? Who is it? The person\Nyou wanted me to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who was waiting in the pouring rain at the tennis court for 4 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is changing into dry clothes\Nright now and will then come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush and just spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is coming here on a bike in this rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to go at it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Jeet Kune Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He dodged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll knock you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We won't give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:35.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A man Sonoko'll be pleased to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and an explosive situation at a bowling alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.21,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:42.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:45.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:31.89,Title,,0,0,0,,The Suspect is Makoto Kyogoku\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll knock you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that person! The one\NSonoko wanted you to meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My boyfriend, Makoto Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This girl is my classmate, Masumi Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were some insolent guy\Nwho was getting overly friendly with Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it! I'm always being mistaken for a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Sonoko! You should have stopped them earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to see those two fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what would you've done if one of them got hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:18.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Here's your glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's no biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to try fighting him a little more too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeet Kune Do... Who taught you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My older brother! Well, my brother was\Nthree times stronger than me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say your older brother was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But weren't you talking on the phone\Nwith your brother the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you overheard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My smart second-oldest brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He takes after our father,\Nunlike my late brother and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he doesn't look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it seems that he's in the middle\Nof an important job right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he won't even tell me where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he sometimes advises me\Non a case on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the case the other day he also told me\Nthat my deduction was unreliable,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but since you were there to\Ncome to the rescue if I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, not me, but Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be that she knows I'm Shin'ichi Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something go wrong\Nwhen you washed that shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The collar is so wide, your underwear is visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's called off-shoulder and it's done on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm showing it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Showing it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That underwear is meant to be shown off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko got all dressed up for you, Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, there's blood\Ncoming from the back of your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that when you\Nfought Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, this is from outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about earlier! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Michiko Mon'na (30)\NMiddle School Math Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. My wounds are very shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's fine. He's simply suffering\Nthe consequences of his actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance is taking him home in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I went to buy some\Nclothes to change into earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I became entangled with an\Nacquaintance of this woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he punched me in the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He may not look it, but he\Nteaches PE at a middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:50.26,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(275,275)}Sunami Masaki (29)\NMiddle School Science Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.47,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Usually Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is an\Nearnest, steady teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when he drinks, he\Nbecomes a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fell asleep in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In his sleep, he whispered,\N"I'm going to kill that bastard."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what are\Nwe going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were going to have him\Nteach us how to bowl, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like you could use a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not let a guy like me\Nshow you how to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use your hips! The hips!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move your hips this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you hold the ball, the pivot leg, ball,\Nand head all need to be in a straight line, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it, magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:08:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, to be able to instruct a couple\Nof teachers. It's the highest honour, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That guy... He'll be brought in\Nfor sexual harassment one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And it seems like this guy will be\Narrested for property damage some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would appear that this sort of\Nfashionable game doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only returned to Japan today,\Nso I also have a bit of jet lag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you\Ntake a nap in Dad's rental car?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing how I have the key...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll take you up on that offer then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when I was finally\Non a date with Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're going out\Nto dinner afterwards as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, where are you going, Michiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to see how Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be back once he sobers up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? He isn't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} wasn't in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, seems like he got out of\Nthe car and went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't he come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe he's sleeping\Nin the shade of some car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking! It's been raining\Nthis whole time, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for someone, why\Ndon't you leave it to me, Kogoro Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father is a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kogoro Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use! He isn't anywhere between the cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he's in some bar, drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He isn't drunkenly bothering\Nsomeone else again, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's look for him in nearby bars, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys go looking\Naround drinking places as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a picture of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I send it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, our rental car was also parked here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Well, I don't think if Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were to get in a fight,\Nhe'd fight back until they were beaten to a pulp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say "beaten to a pulp", at any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! He's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't return to the car either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also turned off his mobile phone, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, where did he disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's that? What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also looked underneath the cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it really seems like he isn't\Nanywhere in this parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then should we ask the police\Nto look for him after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door of the toilet was\Nunlocked, so I opened it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's petechiae on the eyelid and conjunctiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And foam is coming from his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No facial edema.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And no sign of strangulation on the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Death by drowning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Death by drowning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:13.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's also no sign of his having\Nbeen restrained on his arms and legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and since his clothes are soaking wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was carried here after\Nbeing drowned somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, given the state of the livor mortis and\Nrigor mortis, he was killed about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just about the time when we starting looking\Nfor him and went to various drinking places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the killer tossed the corpse\Ninto this toilet and escaped before we returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This teacher's pretty strongly built,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it was either a repeat offender,\Nor someone really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the person who was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was Masahiro Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 32,\Nwho taught PE at a middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one who found the body
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was a science teacher from the same\Nmiddle school, Masaki Sunami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, could you please tell me\Nhow you found him in more detail, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and I had planned to go\Nbowling together with our colleague, Michiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but drunk from the beer he had drunk on the car ride here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he started to act violently\Ndowntown. It was quite stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought it might be best to let him sleep it off, so I brought him to Michiko's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Colleague, you say... Does that mean\Nyou're also a middle school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. I teach math.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Sunami and I had been\Nbowling for about an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the car to check up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a lot of things going on,\Nso I didn't want to leave him on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I came to the car, he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flustered by his disappearance,\Nall of us started looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the bowling alley,\Nwe happened to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None other than me, Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what a pleasant surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we searched the parking lot,\Nbut didn't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thinking that he might be getting drunk again in a bar somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we divided the area between ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with my daughter and her friends helping out as well,\Nand searched in the bars around here for about an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we didn't find him anywhere,\Nso we came back to this parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,thinking that he might have returned to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just as we had thought, he had returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Into this toilet stall on the parking lot,\Nas a cold, drowned corpse, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Drowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Without an autopsy we can't be 100% sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but going from the state of the body,\Nthat is most likely the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the estimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be around 5 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, 5 PM, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's around the time when we left this parking lot\Nto look around the various bars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did you not look inside the toilet\Nthe first time you searched the parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was locked with a padlock, and an\N"out of order" sign was stuck to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stuck to the door, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I saw that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we came to look here for the\Nsecond time that sign had been removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and since the padlock was\Nalso nowhere to be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And when I opened the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means... Between the time when\NSunami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} accompanied the victim to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the time when Michiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} checked up on him\Nan hour later, someone got him away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they drowned him while Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand the others were going around the bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They brought the corpse back here and placed it\Ninside the stall before Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what was that about\Nkeeping watch on Tamba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he becomes like a different person when drunk,\Neasily picking fights with strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he said he wouldn't drink\Neven one today, but in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a bruise on the victim's abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bruise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, my bad, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was drunk and starting an argument\Nover nothing, swung his fist at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I hit him in the solar plexus without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He screamed that our eyes\Nhad met, or something similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are a very good-natured person, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You helped Mr. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the\Nothers looking for that drunk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was taking a nap in Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car,\Nwhich was parked here, at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am taking you into custody for murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait a moment, Yamamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would he really murder someone\Njust because they picked a fight with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He clearly just confessed with\Na cleverness that could rival my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that he has a motive and no alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's not enough to immediately\Narrest him though, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's fumbling along as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!\NThere's no way Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you can prove his innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because... Because Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely fantastic and nice and a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's no proof at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yamamura, please look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a burn mark at the tip of his left shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means the victim was probably\Nknocked out with a stun gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stun gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer used a stun gun,\Nthis guy here should be innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he can knock someone out with\Nnothing but a punch to the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and since the victim was already bruised\Nthere from the first time he punched him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if he used a stun gun\Non purpose to make us think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:19:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that he would walk around with a stun\Ngun for protection, seeing how he's a karate master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Karate master?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been winning championships all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Undefeated in 400 matches,\Nhe's the prince of kicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you should've said so earli—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please say so earlier, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You already met during\Nthe red handkerchief case, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamamura, are you feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sound so formal all of a sudden.\NYou were usually so casual all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I did that on purpose so people\Nwould let their guard down around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as an Inspector I should\Npreserve a certain dignity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you were here the whole time,\Ndid you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspicious person for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was fast asleep, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you were fast asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that the ground\Nis inclined downwards here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's a slight inclination\Ndue to land subsidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like they're planning to work\Non the road surface here next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Land subsidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:25.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a sec! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The slanted dirt marks on this wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:30.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! It's raining again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us go inside the bowling alley for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can continue our talk there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't go soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit strange around the vents there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the only place where the raindrops don't\Nrun down, but form a sort of ring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a bit sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe something was affixed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys should also quickly go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The raindrops are similarly repelled around the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost like it had been weatherized with duct tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this was a drowning, not a suffocation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the same is not true for the\Nvents at the bottom of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's weatherstripping,\Nit makes no sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also, didn't you smell something\Nwhen we first entered the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smell of kerosene!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going now!
